{"title":"Transcend：Detecting Concept Drift in Malware Classification Models论文阅读总结","uid":"43114f1350cad18fe627afc10a1b1c7b","slug":"Transcend","date":"2024-08-30T05:51:09.000Z","updated":"2024-11-08T02:35:19.431Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Transcend.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"Transcend-Detecting-Concept-Drift-in-Malware-Classification-Models\"><a href=\"#Transcend-Detecting-Concept-Drift-in-Malware-Classification-Models\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Transcend: Detecting Concept Drift in Malware Classification Models\"></a><strong>Transcend: Detecting Concept Drift in Malware Classification Models</strong></h1><p>出处：USENIX Security Symposium</p>\n<p>时间：2017</p>\n<h2 id=\"论文概述\"><a href=\"#论文概述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"论文概述\"></a>论文概述</h2><p>针对攻击者不断改良恶意软件带来的概念漂移问题，<strong>本文在模型性能下降之前就进行对退化的检测模型进行识别</strong>，从而及时完成检测模型的更新</p>\n<h2 id=\"现有研究\"><a href=\"#现有研究\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"现有研究\"></a>现有研究</h2><p>传统方法识别模型退化：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>根据模型检测完成后的准确率等指标后顾性判断</li>\n<li>计算测试对象在候选类别中的拟合概率</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"解决方案\"><a href=\"#解决方案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决方案\"></a>解决方案</h2><h3 id=\"Conformal-evaluation（保形评估）\"><a href=\"#Conformal-evaluation（保形评估）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Conformal evaluation（保形评估）\"></a>Conformal evaluation（保形评估）</h3><p><strong>置信度（Confidence）、可信度（Credibility）、不一致性度量都是保形评估的核心。</strong></p>\n<h4 id=\"不一致性度量\"><a href=\"#不一致性度量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"不一致性度量\"></a>不一致性度量</h4><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sonder-Lin/Mypic/img/img/image-20240830155906994.png\" alt=\"image-20240830155906994\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" />\n\n<p><strong>其中评分函数AD即核心的不一致性度量函数</strong></p>\n<p>本文中使用p值作为相似性的度量（P-values as a Similarity Metric）：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sonder-Lin/Mypic/img/img/image-20240830160238815.png\" alt=\"image-20240830160238815\"></p>\n<p>计算式解释：</p>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sonder-Lin/Mypic/img/img/image-20240830160322363.png\" alt=\"image-20240830160322363\" style=\"zoom: 80%;\" />\n\n<h4 id=\"Credibility（可信度）\"><a href=\"#Credibility（可信度）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Credibility（可信度）\"></a>Credibility（可信度）</h4><p><strong>定义：</strong>表示样本与其被分类的类别在统计上的相似程度，即样本属于该类别的可信度。</p>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sonder-Lin/Mypic/img/img/image-20240830162040235.png\" alt=\"image-20240830162040235\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sonder-Lin/Mypic/img/img/image-20240830162409150.png\" alt=\"image-20240830162409150\" style=\"zoom: 80%;\" />\n\n<p><strong>总结：可信度越高，则表明样本在统计上更接近被分类的类别。但存在多类别匹配的局限，即对于多个类别的p值都很高，因此引入置信度</strong></p>\n<h4 id=\"Confidence（置信度）\"><a href=\"#Confidence（置信度）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Confidence（置信度）\"></a>Confidence（置信度）</h4><p><strong>定义：</strong>表示算法对给定分类决策的确信程度，即算法认为该决策正确的程度</p>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sonder-Lin/Mypic/img/img/image-20240830162554801.png\" alt=\"image-20240830162554801\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" />\n\n<p>ps：max括号中的意思是除了已选择的标签的p值，最终得到的是其他标签下的p值最大值</p>\n<h4 id=\"决策评估\"><a href=\"#决策评估\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"决策评估\"></a>决策评估</h4><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sonder-Lin/Mypic/img/img/image-20240830162841888.png\" alt=\"image-20240830162841888\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n\n<p>如果一个算法的决策评估状态是出现高可信度且高置信度的，我们就认为这个算法在决策评估上目前还不错，出现其他情况就说明可能发生了概念漂移。</p>\n","text":"Transcend: Detecting Concept Drift in Malware Classification Models出处：USENIX Sec...","permalink":"/post/Transcend","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":688,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"机器学习","slug":"机器学习","count":3,"path":"api/categories/机器学习.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"概念漂移","slug":"概念漂移","count":1,"path":"api/tags/概念漂移.json"},{"name":"保形预测","slug":"保形预测","count":1,"path":"api/tags/保形预测.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Transcend-Detecting-Concept-Drift-in-Malware-Classification-Models\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Transcend: Detecting Concept Drift in Malware Classification Models</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%87%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">论文概述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%8E%B0%E6%9C%89%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">现有研究</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">解决方案</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Conformal-evaluation%EF%BC%88%E4%BF%9D%E5%BD%A2%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Conformal evaluation（保形评估）</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7%E5%BA%A6%E9%87%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">不一致性度量</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Credibility%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%A1%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Credibility（可信度）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Confidence%EF%BC%88%E7%BD%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Confidence（置信度）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">决策评估</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Sonderlin","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sonder-lin/Mypic/img/img/%E5%A4%B4%E5%83%8F.jpg","link":"/","description":"一位正在重塑知识的小蒟蒻~ <br /> <b><i>过了河便是繁星。</i></b> <br /><br /> @ <b>qq：1425906813</b>","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"对抗攻击1——Evasion attacks against machine learning at test time论文解读","uid":"74